"Paris">Paris</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milan" title=3D=
"Milan">Milan</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barcelona" titl=
e=3D"Barcelona">Barcelona</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cop=
enhagen" title=3D"Copenhagen">Copenhagen</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Moscow" title=3D"Moscow">Moscow</a>, and <a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Paulo" title=3D"S=C3=A3o Paulo">S=C3=A3o Paulo<=
/a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-84" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_note-84"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>84<=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> These openings were in addit=
ion to existing offices in San Francisco, London, <a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Hamburg" title=3D"Hamburg">Hamburg</a>, and <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Berlin" title=3D"Berlin">Berlin</a>.<sup id=3D"ci=
te_ref-85" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Air=
bnb#cite_note-85"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>85<span class=3D"cit=
e-bracket">]</span></a></sup> In September 2013, the company announced that=
 it would establish its European headquarters in <a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/wiki/Dublin" title=3D"Dublin">Dublin</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-86" =
class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_no=
te-86"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>86<span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-87" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"ht=
