t">[</span>87<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>In November 2012, Airbnb opened an office in <a href=3D"https://en.w=
ikipedia.org/wiki/Sydney" title=3D"Sydney">Sydney</a>, its 11th office loca=
tion, and announced plans to launch the service in <a href=3D"https://en.wi=
kipedia.org/wiki/Thailand" title=3D"Thailand">Thailand</a> and <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia" title=3D"Indonesia">Indonesia</a>.<=
sup id=3D"cite_ref-88" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_note-88"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>88<span =
class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> In December 2012, Airbnb opened a=
n office in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Singapore" title=3D"Si=
ngapore">Singapore</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-89" class=3D"reference"><a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_note-89"><span class=3D"cite-=
bracket">[</span>89<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> In April=
 2022, Airbnb instituted a policy of unlimited <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Remote_work" title=3D"Remote work">remote working</a> for almo=
st all its employees.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-90" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_note-90"><span class=3D"cite-bra=
cket">[</span>90<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
