ile-height=3D"3264"></a><figcaption>Airbnb in Toronto</figcaption></figure>
<p>Regulation of short-term rentals can include requirements for hosts to h=
ave business licenses, payment of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
