n.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hotel_industry" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Hotel i=
ndustry">hotel industry</a> has lobbied for stricter regulations on short-t=
erm home rental<sup id=3D"cite_ref-combat_101-0" class=3D"reference"><a hre=
f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Airbnb#cite_note-combat-101"><span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>101<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup=
> and in addition to government-imposed restrictions, many <a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homeowner_association" title=3D"Homeowner associat=
ion">homeowner associations</a> also limit short term rentals.<sup id=3D"ci=
te_ref-102" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ai=
rbnb#cite_note-102"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>102<span class=3D"=
cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
